[LMSROMM:migration] ### Why Migration Cannot Proceed
[LMSROMM:migration] 
[LMSROMM:migration] 1. **Wrong Type of Model**
[LMSROMM:migration]    - LMSROMM is a **probabilistic map matching algorithm** (HMM-based), not a neural network
[LMSROMM:migration]    - LibCity requires deep learning models for traffic prediction (speed, flow, demand)
[LMSROMM:migration]    - This is a localization system for autonomous vehicles, not a traffic forecasting model
